title: Eddie Has A Home Intruder + Lauren Alaina On Losing American Idol + Lunchbox Prank Calls Someone We Didn’t Know Existed
itunes:title: Eddie Has A Home Intruder + Lauren Alaina On Losing American Idol + Lunchbox Prank Calls Someone We Didn’t Know Existed
description:
Eddie tells us about a crazy story about getting woken up in the middle of the night and finding his garage door open. Lauren Alaina stops by to talk about new music, talent competitions she did as a kid and how American Idol was the first contest she ever lost. Plus, Lunchbox pranks called someone because of something he wants to get changed on the internet!
